{
  "stem": "15577.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, on the other side, in the meantime, they got the baths and the showers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, after 45 minutes, they got their clothes back, and it was-- it was called 'disinfected.' And so I-- I was working there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, I was lucky enough to work there, because, first of all, it was a very hard work, because, to, to, to put these things into this ovens, and to take them out, when they were very, very hot, it was a very hard work.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- and, again, I'm jumping-- by the way, I was one of those who got fleck-- or fleck fever or black fever, fleck fever from, from one of the small animals-- which I got there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was a good place to work, because we weren't freezing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could sleep over, there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We weren't obliged to go to-- because we were working also nights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The baths was working 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was powered by, by, by coal-- uh-- uh-- no.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coal!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, there was fire, so we could-- we could boil whatever we-- if we had something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, this was called a very, very good working place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to go to barracks!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- you have to stay in barrack with 200, 300 people in one place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here were a few of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had-- we had a place where we settle our mattresses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We slept on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was warm, nice, and clean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was very, very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was also a very dangerous-- the other side was also dangerous, but, because through the same bathroo-- bath, uh--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--bathhouse were coming the, the watchmans-- the Ukrainians, the Latvians, Lithuanians, were the guards of the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was something to, to, to serve them.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
